Creotime key fob characters

Fabric figures made of cotton in funny shapes with keychain. To decorate with, for example, textile pens. The package contains five different designs, of three pieces each.

Colour: white, black
Length figures: 6-10 cm
Age: from 3 years

15 Keychains
